{"tid":782558,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"耍機心扮分手引意中人注意","createTime":"2018-08-17T00:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T00:00:29.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6957a60da5d5305f2b8ec4708e74837d1c872536","tid":782558,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:00:29.000Z","msg":"女人收兵方法有很多種，日本女性於節目投稿，列出了自己為了變得受歡迎而偷偷地做的事情。<br />\n<br />\n女人為了收兵，究竟可以去到幾盡？日本有節目列出了女性為了變得高人氣，而偷偷地在做的事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1716863/xlarge/e4c230a95eaeaa2784abd3c001e2d52f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1716863%2Fxlarge%2Fe4c230a95eaeaa2784abd3c001e2d52f.jpg&h=281649f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「收兵」這個文化<br />\n不只是香港才有。<br />\n有日本女性於節目投稿，<br />\n道出自己為了變得受歡迎，<br />\n暗地裡做的事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1716953/xlarge/18c891414f119640cf5e3637927ec3c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1716953%2Fxlarge%2F18c891414f119640cf5e3637927ec3c4.jpg&h=6a2caacb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>【1】扮分手引注意</strong><br />\n<br />\n其中一個投稿的女性指，<br />\n她在公司裡有喜歡的人，<br />\n於是就抓緊他回家的時間。<br />\n裝著在他面前與男友說分手，<br />\n引起他的注意及關心。<br />\n然後在第2日，<br />\n刻意在他面前，<br />\n表現得非常開朗，<br />\n結果他就邀請自己一起喝酒，<br />\n又說「有煩惱的話可以跟我傾訴喔」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1717025/xlarge/cdc3dbe2f27f3eece5367eecc69173c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1717025%2Fxlarge%2Fcdc3dbe2f27f3eece5367eecc69173c9.jpg&h=a99ecf56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>【2】面對告白從不拒絕</strong><br />\n<br />\n當遇到不喜歡的人向自己告白，<br />\n大部分人都會立即拒絕。<br />\n但這個日本妹子不會拒絕，<br />\n反而對他說「告白得太遲了」，<br />\n如果能再早一點說的話，<br />\n他們就能在一起了。<br />\n既不會讓那個男生難堪，<br />\n又能留下一線，<br />\n令到對方不會放棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1717072/xlarge/6ed8cbf5323498ee41855fd58bf84811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1717072%2Fxlarge%2F6ed8cbf5323498ee41855fd58bf84811.jpg&h=f5bcb34b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>【3】對大叔都要投其所好</strong><br />\n<br />\n當與一群大叔聯誼時，<br />\n被問到「你們喜歡的藝人是誰？」，<br />\n不要說年輕的帥氣演員，<br />\n試著說出不年輕又不帥的藝人，<br />\n令他們覺得自己也有機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://opener.hk01.com/%E5%85%A9%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA/218865/%E8%80%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%BF%83%E6%89%AE%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9F-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A6%B9%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A03%E6%8B%9B%E6%94%B6%E5%85%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopener.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%2F218865%2F%25E8%2580%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2589%25AE%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A03%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25B5&d=A7mLzLvfcAnHC%2Bsm7SmLdzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=71f64aa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://opener.hk01.com/%E5%85%A9%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA/218865/%E8%80%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%BF%83%E6%89%AE%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9F-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A6%B9%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A03%E6%8B%9B%E6%94%B6%E5%85%B5</a>"}]}